# Pizza Ingredient Rain Game

Welcome to the **Pizza Ingredient Rain Game**! This is a fun and interactive game where pizza ingredients (emojis) fall from the sky, and you can interact with them using your mouse.

## Features

- 🍕 **Pizza-themed emojis**: Watch ingredients like cheese, tomatoes, mushrooms, and more rain down.
- 🖱️ **Mouse interaction**: Move your mouse to control the falling ingredients.
- 🎮 **Dynamic gameplay**: Emojis accumulate and interact with the canvas environment.
- 🐉 **Custom cursor**: A fun emoji cursor adds a playful touch to the game.

## How to Play

1. Open the game in your browser.
2. Move your mouse to start the rain of pizza ingredients.
3. Click and drag to interact with the falling emojis.
4. Watch as the ingredients pile up and create a pizza-themed chaos!

## Installation

1. Clone this repository to your local machine:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/lluvia-de-ingredientes-pizza.git